name: Jewels of the Sea
description: As an Eastern Coast beachcomber, seashells are indeed "Jewels of the Sea" to me. Always wearing my jeweled shades to "see" the seashells. Even the seashells wear jeweled shades to be seen as seashells. So, how many seashells do you see?  🐚The seashells shown in the digital art washed onto the Atlantic Coast beaches of Ocean City, Maryland USA.  🐚 🐚 Please note: Buyer(s) have the right to own, sell, lend, or otherwise transfer the NFT itself.
